Package: xtpretest
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Panel Data Pre-Testing Suite
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Muhammad", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive suite of pre-tests for panel data
    analysis. Implements Hsiao (2014) homogeneity tests (F1, F2, F3) for
    slope and intercept equality, heteroscedasticity-robust variants,
    Swamy (1970) parameter heterogeneity test, and Pesaran (2004) built-in
    cross-sectional dependence test. Produces formatted summary tables,
    variance decomposition (between vs within), coefficient heterogeneity
    statistics, and a model recommendation based on the sequential testing
    strategy. Hsiao, C. (2014) <doi:10.1017/CBO9781139839327>. Swamy,
    P. A. V. B. (1970) <doi:10.2307/1909405>. Pesaran, M. H. (2004)
    <doi:10.2139/ssrn.572504>.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
